<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Invoice #<%= invoice.invoiceNumber %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .clinic-info {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .invoice-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .patient-info {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .amount-due {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e74c3c;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1><%= clinicName %></h1>
    <p><%= clinicAddress %></p>
    <p>Phone: <%= clinicPhone %> | Email: <%= clinicEmail %></p>
  </div>

  <h2>Invoice #<%= invoice.invoiceNumber %></h2>
  <p>Date: <%= new Date(invoice.invoiceDate).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
  <p>Due Date: <%= new Date(invoice.dueDate).toLocaleDateString() %></p>

  <div class="patient-info">
    <h3>Bill To:</h3>
    <p><strong><%= invoice.patientName || invoice.patient.name %></strong></p>
    <p><%= invoice.patient.email || invoice.patientId?.email %></p>
    <p><%= invoice.patient.phone || invoice.patientId?.phone %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="invoice-details">
    <h3>Invoice Summary</h3>
    <p>Subtotal: $<%= (invoice.subtotal / 100).toFixed(2) %></p>
    <% if (invoice.tax > 0) { %>
      <p>Tax (<%= invoice.taxRate || 0 %>%): $<%= (invoice.tax / 100).toFixed(2) %></p>
    <% } %>
    <% if (invoice.discount > 0) { %>
      <p>Discount: -$<%= (invoice.discount / 100).toFixed(2) %></p>
    <% } %>
    <p class="amount-due">Amount Due: $<%= (invoice.total / 100).toFixed(2) %></p>
    <p>Status: <strong><%= invoice.status %></strong></p>
  </div>

  <p>Please find attached a copy of your invoice for your records.</p>
  <p>You can also view your invoice and make payments online through our patient portal.</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="<%= process.env.PATIENT_PORTAL_URL || '#' %>" class="button">Pay Now</a>
  </div>

  <p>If you have any questions about this invoice, please don't hesitate to contact our office.</p>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>© <%= currentYear %> <%= clinicName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This email was sent to <%= invoice.patient.email || invoice.patientId?.email %>. 
    If you believe you received this in error, please contact us.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
